<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-05-17T16:48:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-05-17T16:48:00-05:00" n="392" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d392">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/4723</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_EJ1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Ewing</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Tegucigalpa</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-05-17T16:00:00-05:48">
                                        <hi rend="italic">May 17, 1917, 4 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 9 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>The President to-day decrees adherence to United States and
                                diplomatic relations with the German Government broken, followed by
                                second decree regarding public safety declaring Republic in <hi rend="italic">estado de sitio</hi>.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_EJ1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ewing</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>